-- India Extends Ban on Imports of Chinese Milk, Milk-Products by Six Months
-- Thomas Abraham
-- 2010-06-24T06:44:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/india-extends-ban-on-imports-of-chinese-milk-milk-products-by-six-months.html

          
          
             India extended a ban on imports of
milk and milk products from China for a further six months, the
Ministry of Commerce and Industry said today in a statement on
its website.  
 The ban includes chocolates, confectionary and foods
prepared with milk or milk solids, the ministry said. The ban
was imposed in December 2008, it said.  
